        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis needs a corresponding change in oom.  In  Frankfurt, we mount the cert as a secret (see https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/oom/+/109761).  For Guilin, we should instead use certInitializer to create the SSL certificate.\n\nMarking this as WIP as a reminder not to merge until OOM piece is ready.",
